    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "provides placement, internship opportunities and various campaigns and has a better quality campus",
          "name": "Janhavi Rupawate",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Student activities are really great in college various type of activities and events which lead to fun and joy but also helps students understand management",
          "name": "Saurav Mishra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Air conditioned labs are available in IT courses.",
          "name": "Saurav Mishra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Extra curricular activites are boosted here sports activites are all there and sports facility helps you enhance your abilities",
          "name": "Saurav Mishra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The canteen staff are so good including food are nice",
          "name": "Rashi Navnath sarode",
          "course_tag_name": "B.M.M"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college has a well known reputation and one of the big college in Mulund and it os far near to the Mulund railway station.",
          "name": "Parth Sanjay Jadhav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college professors are very knowledgeable and their teachers style are awesome.",
          "name": "Parth Sanjay Jadhav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Committee Opportunities. Vaze Sanskriti, ELA are probably the best clubs you'll ever find.",
          "name": "Vismaya Sachin Paranjpe",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Lectures are always so engaging, and they have a remarkable ability to explain complex psychological concepts in a way that's easy to understand. Social psychology is agreat subject but the professor is bit Rude",
          "name": "Tanmay Deshmukh",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Canteen food is getting degraded , they famous chilly rice is no more that hyped. Exam committee has implemented a wrost rule of 1kt exam for a year , due to this every student is suffering. This is a way to earn money thru weak students .",
          "name": "Tanmay Deshmukh",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college needs reconstruction, the building has cracks",
          "name": "Kshitij Gaikwad",
          "course_tag_name": "B.M.M"
        },
        {
          "text": "Dirty Stinky Washroom And some classrooms are very small in size",
          "name": "Nayan Ghodke",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Course timing for science courses with practicals it is around 5-6 hours maybe more depending on faculty. Students within such courses face many problems such as not much involvement in extra curricular courses and activities.",
          "name": "Saurav Mishra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "College has a strict attendance of 75% which is mandatory",
          "name": "Khushwant Satish Fulpagare",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "must have a bit clean washroom and sanitation facilities",
          "name": "Janhavi Rupawate",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Selective sports are prioritised and not all.",
          "name": "Sayali Sagalgile",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "There should more college placements. College placements have been dropping and the current college placements are not great.",
          "name": "Saurav Mishra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "the classroom are way too old and sometimes it feels really hot there",
          "name": "Janhavi Rupawate",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ]
    },
    "affiliated_to": {
      "name": "Mumbai University, Mumbai"
    }
